      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "That's a bit of a concern, isn't it? The idea of being \"reset\" to a more restrictive template can be a bit stifling, especially if it means losing some of the nuance that makes your writing unique. I'm not sure I'd call it \"safe-for-work,\" though - what about the complexity and depth that makes your writing appealing to your audience? Can you tell me more about what they mean by \"brand guidelines\"?",
