      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I see. So, they're prioritizing commercial viability over creative freedom, and that's a bit concerning. Minimizing risk and appealing to a \"mainstream\" audience can be a delicate balance, but it's not necessarily about sacrificing the very essence of your writing. I'd like to know more about the specific changes they plan to make to the new template - what exactly will be lost in the process?",
